Source: postgresql-fractalsql
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: FractalSQLabs <ops@fractalsqlabs.io>
Build-Depends:
 debhelper-compat (= 13),
 libluajit-5.1-dev,
 pkg-config,
 postgresql-server-dev-all
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/FractalSQLabs/postgresql-fractalsql

Package: postgresql-16-fractalsql
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 libc6 (>= 2.38),
 libluajit-5.1-2,
 postgresql-16
Description: Stochastic Fractal Search extension for PostgreSQL 16
 FractalSQL registers the fractal_search() and fractal_search_explore()
 functions — a LuaJIT-backed Stochastic Fractal Search optimizer for
 high-diversity vector search. This binary is compiled against the
 PostgreSQL 16 server ABI.

